  "prompt": "Is Narendra Modi on Quora?",
  "response": "As of my knowledge up to October 2023, **Narendra Modi**, the Prime Minister of India, does not maintain an official or verified presence on **Quora**. While Quora hosts a vast number of users who may ask questions about him or discuss his policies and initiatives, any profiles directly attributed to him are likely unofficial or managed by fans and supporters.\n\nFor official updates, statements, and interactions from Prime Minister Narendra Modi, it is best to refer to his verified social media accounts or official government channels, such as:\n\n- **Twitter:** [@narendramodi](https://twitter.com/narendramodi)\n- **Facebook:** [Narendra Modi](https://www.facebook.com/narendramodi)\n- **Official Website:** [narendramodi.in](https://www.narendramodi.in/)\n\nThese platforms are regularly updated with accurate and authorized information directly from the Prime Minister's office.",
